(15463, 296, '_crb_post_section|crb_blog_paragraph|4|0|value', '<p class=\"zm-clr-gr4c fnt-21 fnt-bitter mb-3\">We have vaccinated over 200 workers at our Trichy factory in association with the State Industries Promotion Corporation of Tamil Nadu (SIPCOT). We have also vaccinated 30% of Zetwerks employees and their immediate family members in Bengaluru. We aim to cover the majority of our employees through this drive at the earliest</p>'),
