(33047, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list|1|3|value', '_'),
(33048, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list|1:0|0|value', 'Open Die Forging'),
(33049, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list_items|1:0|0|value', 'Zetwerk utilizes open die forging to hammer into shape parts as large as 150T and 25 metres in weight and height respectively. This process allows for open die forging of all forgeable ferrous and non-ferrous alloys,including exotic materials like age-hardening superalloys and corrosion-resistant refractory alloys.'),
(33050, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list|1:1|0|value', 'Closed Die Forging'),
(33051, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list_items|1:1|0|value', 'For complex shapes and tighter tolerances, Zetwerk employs closed die forging using two or more dies containing impressions of the part shape. Engineering metals and alloys like carbon and alloy steels, tool steels, stainless, aluminum and copper alloys and titanium alloys can be forged through closed die forging.'),
(33052, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list|1:2|0|value', 'Cold Forging'),
(33053, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list_items|1:2|0|value', 'While most forging is done as hot work, Zetwerk is also proficient in cold forging processes like bending, cold drawing, cold heading, coining and extrusions to create a diverse range of part shapes. The output is forged parts that have enhanced dimensional control, product uniformity and surface finish.'),
(33054, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list|1:3|0|value', 'Rolled Ring Forging'),
(33055, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_post_menufac_sec_list:crb_manufac_hero_list_items|1:3|0|value', '<p class=\"fnt-21 zw-section-lead__des zm-clr-gr4c my-3\">Zetwerk performs rolled ring forging by punching a hole in a thick, round piece of metal, and then rolling and squeezing the metal into a thin ring. Ring diameters vary from less than a meter to over 10 meter</p>'),
(33056, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_heading|2|0|value', 'FINISHING TOUCHES'),
(33057, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_sub_text|2|0|value', 'Zetwerk offers necessary secondary operations on the forged parts such as finish machining, heat treatment and surface treatment. Its quality-driven process ensures that the forged parts meet exact specifications of material chemistry, dimensional accuracy, mechanical properties, and structural integrity. Forging heat treatment services include normalizing, annealing, quenching, tempering, stress relieving, spheroidize annealing, solution annealing, solution heat treating and straightening. Zetwerk also provides a host of mechanical, metallurgical and non-destructive testing services to make sure that the produced parts meet quality standards.'),
(33058, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_section_bg|2|0|value', '1'),
(33059, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_img|2|0|value', 'http://localhost:8888/zetwerk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/finishing-touch-forging-1.png'),
(33060, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_section_img_overlay|2|0|value', '2'),
(33061, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_heading|3|0|value', 'QUALITY CONTROL AND ASSEMBLY'),
(33062, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_sub_text|3|0|value', 'Zetwerks Quality Control includes testing and heat treatment of cast components. Salt Spray tests and Hydrostatic and Pneumatic pressure tests determine the corrosion resistance of the die casting. For ease of assembly, Zetwerk also offers the produced parts in a sub-assembly along with hardware and other components necessary for assembly.'),
(33063, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_section_bg|3|0|value', '2'),
(33064, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_tri_sec_img|3|0|value', 'http://localhost:8888/zetwerk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/quality-control.png'),
(33065, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|manufac_section_img_overlay|3|0|value', '1'),
(33066, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_client_logo_heading|4|0|value', 'QUALITY CERTIFICATIONS'),
(33067, 478, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_client_logo_sub_text|4|0|value', '<p class=\"zw-section-lead__des zm-clr-gr4c mt-md-2\">Zetwerk is ISO 9001:2015 and AS9100D certified. Its forging plants are IATF 16949:2016 certified.</p>'),
