(37846, 535, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_indust_slider:manufac_service_section_sub_text|1:2|0|value', 'Zetwerk is supplying and erecting steel structures along and deck panels for ISRO Propulsion Complex (IPRC) in Mahendragiri, which will be the hub of propulsion technology products for the Indian space programme.'),
