(52091, 536, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_indust_slider:manufac_service_section_sub_text|1:1|0|value', 'Zetwerk is helping set up the Nuclear Fuel Complex in Kota to serve the upcoming nuclear reactors. It is providing fabrication, erection, testing and commissioning of pipe rack structural works for the facility.'),
