(53530, 545, '_crb_manufac_banner_title', 'SAND CASTING'),
(53531, 545, '_crb_manufac_banner_sub_text', 'Zetwerks sand casting services are a cost-efficient method for producing small and large parts from various ferrous and non-ferrous alloys. The process is calibrated to produce large scale workpieces in high volumes and for short run work.'),
