(54036, 470, '_crb_manufac_banner_title', 'FORGING'),
(54037, 470, '_crb_manufac_banner_sub_text', 'Zetwerks proven experience in forging serves some of the most operationally demanding manufacturing requirements. With cutting-edge design tools, software and a global network of skilled partners, Zetwerk produces high quality forged components, progressing from prototypes in open die forging to hardened steel closed die mass production, resulting in shorter lead times.'),
