(57606, 494, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_indust_slider:manufac_service_section_sub_text|1:0|0|value', 'Zetwerk has a dedicated Fabric and Trim sourcing team for knits and wovens for both denims and non-denims. It partners with fabrics mills in India and abroad to develop proprietary CAD designs to create a variety of designs for a single fabric. Zetwerk also works towards sustainability, and has certified sustainable fabric connections.'),
