(60115, 735, '_crb_careers_banner_heading', 'PEOPLE-POWERED MANUFACTURING'),
(60116, 735, '_crb_careers_banner_subtxt', 'Zetwerks team of industry experts have an unmatched mix of skills and experience from operationally demanding business environments that range from surface logistics to strategic consulting. Team Zetwerks combined experience represents global best practices and grassroots know-how across industries, sectors and geographies.'),
