(67285, 766, '_crb_careers_gtitle', 'RISE IN GOOD COMPANY'),
(67286, 766, '_crb_careers_gsubtxt', '<p class=\"my-3\">A company that\'s changing the way manufacturing is done needs game changers to shape the future. At Zetwerk, our job is to help you excel in your career. We offer you an environment to create a unique career journey, opportunities to grow your ambition and an inclusive culture to help you thrive.</p>\r\n<p class=\"my-3\">We encourage innovation through collaboration and connect you to leaders who help you in your overall growth. We facilitate direct interface with leadership for overall growth of the company as well as employees.</p>\r\n<p class=\"my-3\">We offer best-in-industry culture and practices for a complete peace of mind for you and your family. We deliver the best for our people so that they can deliver the best for our customers. It\'s that simple. It\'s Zetwerk.</p>\r\n<p class=\"my-3\">Zetwerk is among the fastest growing companies in India, with a 40% MoM and an annual growth rate of 300%. We\'re backed by some of the leading VC firms in the world such as D1 Capital Partners, Green Oaks, Lightspeed, Sequoia Capital, Accel Partners and Kae Capital.</p>'),
