(68237, 430, '_crb_manufact_section|crb_manufac_indust_slider:manufac_service_section_sub_text|1:0|0|value', 'To smoothen the parting line and remove gates, overflows and flash, die-cast components are vibrated and tumbled. Thermal deburring is used to remove burrs and other imperfections from die cast parts.'),
